{"title":"战斗的青春放光彩","authors":["张永枚"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":12,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗的青春放光彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三朵鲜花向阳开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三棵树儿迎风栽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条船上三姐妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东海前线常往来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱跳爱唱是小三妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮火下开出一枝梅："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上支援前线留下她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噘起小嘴喊倒霉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹们划船到海心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船舱底下歌声飞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭开船板看——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊？啥呀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舱底下跳出个小三妹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大姐二姐你来看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一只海鹰虽然小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她迎着风浪能高飞！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎嗨哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小妹今年刚满十五岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮火下支援前线上千回！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二姐本是个女老?，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪里穿梭云里来："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天她喊声有情况，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举鲨鱼钩跳下海！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听海水哗啦啦响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪头打到船上来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二姐上了船——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用力拉呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲨鱼钩钓起个“水鬼”来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大姐三妹别奇怪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚才我见这儿直冒泡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就知这‘鲨鱼’要来破坏！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎嗨哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心明眼亮手脚快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二姐的胆量大过东海！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的大姐像块钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有硬来又有柔："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平时讲话嗓门细，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一天讲话如雷吼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震得东海千尺浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震得敌人抬不起头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮难开口——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊？啥呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她是咱们的一炮手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三姐妹，雄赳赳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国的妇女多自豪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打得那瘟神夹着尾巴就逃走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎嗨哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反帝的大旗高高举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三姐妹一齐奋勇战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三朵鲜花向阳开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三棵树儿迎风栽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产战斗双跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹们在炮火中成长起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的时代新妇女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗的青春放光彩！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}